      "writtenOn": "2020-12-17T22:27:27Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I should mention if we do it this way we\u0027ll see how the program would behave as if writing to 4 float planes.  We can change that up of course if you like,\n\n    const SkColorType ct \u003d kRGBA_F32_SkColorType;  // or whatever\n\n    skvm::PixelFormat fmt;\n    SkColorType_to_PixelFormat(ct, \u0026fmt);\n    store(fmt, builder.arg(SkColorTypeBytesPerPixel(ct)), result));",
      "revId": "a89ade1dde2feac9473bd5eb1dc0e234156c15a8",
